name: Gan356 Air SM
description:
Magnets in AirSM will not drop, and their positions will be more precise with the
      Magnets-Snap-On design. With the use of 3mm*2mm magnets, the handfeel will be more stable and more
      comfortable. P.S. This design is brand new for the AirSM.

name: MAGIC CUBE
description: When the Hungarian Erno Rubik invented the Rubik's Cube in 1974, it was said that he wanted to train students in spatial thinking. But we suspect he just wanted to put the patience of all humanity to the test!
